<sect1 id="dataloader_page_1dataloader_intro">
<title>Introduction</title>
<para>The <ref refid="classdataloader" kindref="compound">dataloader</ref> class manages efficient data loading, batching, and k-fold cross-validation for machine learning training and evaluation. It handles graph data transfer between CPU and GPU devices.</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="dataloader_page_1dataloader_inheritance">
<title>Inheritance</title>
<para><programlisting><codeline><highlight class="normal"><ref refid="classnotification" kindref="compound">notification</ref></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>└──┐</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>├──<sp/><ref refid="classdataloader" kindref="compound">dataloader</ref></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>│</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><ref refid="classtools" kindref="compound">tools</ref><sp/>─┘</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="dataloader_page_1dataloader_features">
<title>Features</title>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para><bold>K-fold Cross-Validation</bold>: Automatic data splitting for cross-validation</para>
</listitem><listitem><para><bold>Train/Test Splitting</bold>: Configurable train/test split ratios</para>
</listitem><listitem><para><bold>Batch Construction</bold>: Efficient batching of graph data</para>
</listitem><listitem><para><bold>GPU Data Transfer</bold>: Automatic tensor transfer to CUDA devices</para>
</listitem><listitem><para><bold><ref refid="classGraph" kindref="compound">Graph</ref> Serialization</bold>: Save/restore graph datasets to/from HDF5</para>
</listitem><listitem><para><bold>CUDA Memory Server</bold>: Background memory management for GPUs</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</sect1>
