<sect1 id="dataloader_page_1dataloader_batching">
<title>Batching Details</title>
<para>The <computeroutput>build_batch()</computeroutput> method constructs batched graphs by:</para>
<para><orderedlist>
<listitem><para><bold>Collecting Graphs</bold>: Gather N graphs for the batch</para>
</listitem><listitem><para><bold>Concatenating Nodes</bold>: Stack all node features [Σn_i, F]</para>
</listitem><listitem><para><bold>Adjusting <ref refid="classEdge" kindref="compound">Edge</ref> Indices</bold>: Offset edge indices for batched graph</para>
</listitem><listitem><para><bold>Creating Batch Index</bold>: Track which nodes belong to which graph</para>
</listitem><listitem><para><bold>Stacking <ref refid="classGraph" kindref="compound">Graph</ref> Features</bold>: Combine graph-level features [N, G]</para>
</listitem></orderedlist>
</para>
<para>The resulting batched graph is compatible with PyTorch Geometric conventions.</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="dataloader_page_1dataloader_kfold_details">
<title>K-Fold Cross-Validation</title>
<para>The dataloader supports stratified k-fold cross-validation:</para>
<para><programlisting filename=".cpp"><codeline><highlight class="normal"><ref refid="classdataloader" kindref="compound">dataloader</ref><sp/>dl;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>Generate<sp/>5-fold<sp/>splits<sp/>with<sp/>80%<sp/>train,<sp/>20%<sp/>test</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">dl.<ref refid="classdataloader_1a086338e3e9670d253041f54888995611" kindref="member">generate_test_set</ref>(20);<sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>20%<sp/>for<sp/>final<sp/>test</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">dl.<ref refid="classdataloader_1ac35a068b2e42d77b1fe986c65e3c2d24" kindref="member">generate_kfold_set</ref>(5);<sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>5<sp/>folds<sp/>from<sp/>remaining<sp/>80%</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="keywordflow">for</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>(</highlight><highlight class="keywordtype">int</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>k<sp/>=<sp/>0;<sp/>k<sp/>&lt;<sp/>5;<sp/>++k)<sp/>{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="keyword">auto</highlight><highlight class="normal">*<sp/>train<sp/>=<sp/>dl.<ref refid="classdataloader_1ae243f6005ad6f4e2600b44d7ee6d40ed" kindref="member">get_k_train_set</ref>(k);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="keyword">auto</highlight><highlight class="normal">*<sp/>valid<sp/>=<sp/>dl.<ref refid="classdataloader_1a132ebd49d79e9339c2aa96ba9cfd6bc7" kindref="member">get_k_validation_set</ref>(k);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>Train<sp/>on<sp/>train,<sp/>validate<sp/>on<sp/>valid</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">}</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="keyword">auto</highlight><highlight class="normal">*<sp/>test<sp/>=<sp/>dl.<ref refid="classdataloader_1a7a0c887638c888df9b55cbdf45c816c9" kindref="member">get_test_set</ref>();</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>Final<sp/>evaluation<sp/>on<sp/>test</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="dataloader_page_1dataloader_serialization">
<title>Graph Serialization</title>
<para>Graphs can be serialized to HDF5 for faster subsequent loading:</para>
<para><programlisting filename=".cpp"><codeline><highlight class="normal"><ref refid="classdataloader" kindref="compound">dataloader</ref><sp/>dl;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>...<sp/>populate<sp/>with<sp/>graphs<sp/>...</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>Save<sp/>to<sp/>disk</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">dl.<ref refid="classdataloader_1a04c94d9be735c32b80b6599c6bd993b4" kindref="member">dump_graphs</ref>(</highlight><highlight class="stringliteral">&quot;./graph_cache/&quot;</highlight><highlight class="normal">,<sp/>10);<sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>10<sp/>threads</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>Later:<sp/>restore<sp/>from<sp/>disk</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><ref refid="classdataloader" kindref="compound">dataloader</ref><sp/>dl2;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">dl2.<ref refid="classdataloader_1aed6ec872879a44ecfa9ae1c2188690a8" kindref="member">restore_graphs</ref>(</highlight><highlight class="stringliteral">&quot;./graph_cache/&quot;</highlight><highlight class="normal">,<sp/>10);</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
<para><simplesect kind="see"><para><ref refid="structgraph__t" kindref="compound">graph_t</ref> </para>
